data.description: Very private w/beautiful trees, house sits far back from the road. Beautiful views of the lake from most windows. Enjoy looking at the lake while at the kitchen sink. Kitchen was remodeled w/new counters with oak trim, new appliances, new cooktop, oven, & refrigerator. Next to the kitchen is the dining area w/sliders to upper deck which gives a beautiful view of lake while dining. Master bath totally gutted, everything new w/beadboard walls, granite countertop & new fixtures. Lower level family room has a nice fireplace and sliding doors lead to a lower deck. There is a new metal roof and sump pump (2021) and several new windows (2015). There are steps down to the water and a boat dock. Amenities of a community pool, clubhouse, tennis courts and sand volleyball and of course the lake make this a great family neighborhood. Cinnamon Lake is located in the scenic heart of Ohio Amish country. Situated in the Northeastern part of Ashland County just outside of West Salem. Over 1200 acres encompass the private development which includes over 200 acres of common areas and a 135 acre lake. Amenities include a 4,500 sq. ft. lodge, a beach & swimming pool, basketball court, tennis courts, sand volleyball & a playground. Wet & dry docks for use are available for a fee to members. Golf carts are allowed. The lake is stocked w/bass, walleye, saugeye, crappie, & bluegill to name a few!
